data.description: Ready to move in 1.5 story home that offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a private backyard. The neighborhood is walkable to the Southern Boone elementary and primary schools. It is also close to Ashland's restaurants and new and upcoming business. The home offers custom cabinets, a large kitchen, an oversized master bedroom closet, a master bathroom that has double vanities and a jetted tub and a fenced in backyard.
